    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SAIL上基于elmos，新增TB185方案"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "假设："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "100khz时钟芯片方案 follow elmos 500khz",
        "AS负责TB185功能安全/降级，ESW2只负责TB185供电和SPI驱动"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "工作内容："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "1. TB185上电 LCM   1week"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "2.  TB185的clock生成需要配置成另一路有源时钟芯片（前提是采用100K的有源时钟芯片方案）1 week"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "3.  SPI 需要配置TB185的通道  3week"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "4.  Variant实现，宏或者KDS   2week"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "5. Elmos 和TB185 两种方案，适配AS对底软的依赖接口 4week"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "6.  bugfix     1week"
    }
  ],
